data.description: This is a very clean sun-drenched Southern-exposure townhome in great condition!  Private End-unit with views of the pond and no other homes in close proximity! Huge Center-island kitchen with breakfast bar, pantry, and large dining area with sliding door to exterior patio!  2 story living room with tons of windows!  Upper Loft is large enough for a second hanging out space! Custom shower in Primary bath upstairs!  Easy access to Pilot knob and the new Lunds/Byerlys is just 5 minutes away! Flexible closing!   See photos!
